text: Yaohai is a district in the province of Anhui in China. The district has 902,830 people.Compilation by LianXin website. Data from the Sixth National Population Census of the People's Republic of China It contains 1 township, 1 town, 10 subdistricts, 1 industrial park, and 1 development zone. ==References== Category:Districts of China Category:Anhui
title: Yaohai District
